<book>
  <chapter id="welcome-4.1">
    <title>Welcome to Product X</title>
    <para>Welcome to the 2.0 release of  X, the second major release from the Apache CloudStack
      project since its graduation from the Apache Incubator. X includes more than 50 new features
      and enhancements. The focus of the release is on three major areas:</para>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>Improved support for both legacy-style and cloud-style workloads</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>New third-party plug-in architecture</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>Networking enhancements</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </chapter>
</book>
